 ✅ To-Do List App

A simple || To-Do List || web application built with | HTML | CSS | JavaScript | . It allows users to add, edit, delete, and mark tasks as completed. Perfect for managing daily tasks!


---

 📋 Features

- ✅ Add tasks
- ✏️ Edit tasks
- ❌ Delete tasks
- ✔️ Mark tasks as completed
- 🔄 Store tasks in localStorage (persistent across sessions)
- 🖥️ Fully responsive UI for all devices

---

🛠️ Technologies Used

- | HTML5 | – Structure and layout  
- | CSS3 | – Styling and responsiveness  
- | JavaScript (ES6) | – Functionality and DOM manipulation  
- | localStorage |– Store tasks for persistence  

